```plantuml
@startuml NicoJuicy_Airline-Microservices

package "Airline Microservices System" {
    [API Gateway] as ApiGateway
    [Identity Service] as IdentityService
    [Flight Service] as FlightService
    [Passenger Service] as PassengerService
    [Reservation Service] as ReservationService

    package "Shared Components" {
        [Building Blocks] as BuildingBlocks
        [MassTransit] as MassTransit
        [RabbitMQ] as RabbitMQ
    }
}

ApiGateway --> IdentityService : routes/auth
ApiGateway --> FlightService : routes/flights
ApiGateway --> PassengerService : routes/passengers
ApiGateway --> ReservationService : routes/reservations

IdentityService --> BuildingBlocks : uses
FlightService --> BuildingBlocks : uses
PassengerService --> BuildingBlocks : uses
ReservationService --> BuildingBlocks : uses

IdentityService ..> RabbitMQ : publishes events
FlightService ..> RabbitMQ : publishes/subscribes
PassengerService ..> RabbitMQ : publishes/subscribes
ReservationService ..> RabbitMQ : publishes/subscribes

RabbitMQ ..> MassTransit : message broker

note top of BuildingBlocks
    Contains:
    - Common utilities
    - Exception handling
    - Logging (Serilog)
    - Swagger config
    - Messaging abstractions
    - Security components
end note

note right of MassTransit
    Implements:
    - Event-driven communication
    - Integration events
end note

@enduml
```